nodes.text: Mon Calamari Squiduariums were a type of fish tank produced by the Mon Calamari, a species from the ocean world of Dac. Squiduariums had a certain degree of popularity during the Clone Wars.
Mon Calamari Squiduariums appeared in the massively multiplayer online game Star Wars: Clone Wars Adventures as part of the "Mon Calamari Furniture Set."
